What you need to know:

This weekend, the world has once again witnessed the unique grandeur of motorsport in Kenya, the unparalleled fan enthusiasm of our Nation, and the sporting excellence of the various teams through this great Safari Rally.Driven by the hunger of Kenyans for the return of top tier motorsport to Kenya, in 2013 I promised our nation that we would end the 11-years of relegation from the International Automobile Federation circuit.